snippet.title: Epistemology & the Making of Sense - Daniel Schmachtenberger at the Buckminster Fuller Institute
snippet.description:
Original available here (Unlisted as of August 19th, 2020): https://youtu.be/xecdaZhH4Nw

This was re-uploaded from the Unlisted original for educational purposes only. If you own this material and would like it unlisted, let us know in the comments.

The playlist titled "Essentials at The Seeking" on this channel offers a collection of clips discussing what may be deemed some of the most fundamental concepts to our endeavor.
